OL,4,Ccyberstalking
OL,6,FA woman who relentlessly stalked a
OL,7,Fmotivational speaker and businesswoman
OL,8,Fonline has been jailed.
OL,10,FSamantha Wall, 55, has been sentenced
OL,11,Fto 28 months, after she pleaded guilty
OL,12,Fat an earlier hearing to stalking and
OL,13,Fharassing motivational speaker Brad
OL,14,FBurton and businesswoman Naomi
OL,15,FTimperley, who are both from Greater
OL,16,FManchester.
OL,18,FWall's sentence comes after years of
OL,19,Frelentless online posts in which she
OL,20,Fmade false claims about both victims.
