OL,3,CWoman sentenced after 'horrific'
OL,4,Ccyberstalking
OL,6,FTwo years after briefly meeting Brad
OL,7,FBurton at a business event, she began
OL,8,Fmaking online posts containing false
OL,9,Fclaims that he poisoned her cat, made
OL,10,Fdeath threats against her, put a
OL,11,Ftracking device on her, broke her
OL,12,Fwindows and slashed her tires.
OL,14,FSpeaking outside of court, Mr Burton
OL,15,Fsaid: "This has been a tough, tough
OL,16,Ffive years. There's other victims that
OL,17,Fcame forward to us... this is for
OL,18,Fthem."
