OL,6,FMr Burton described the impact of
OL,7,FWall's stalking as "traumatic", and
OL,8,F"devastating" for his mental health.
OL,10,FHe said: "The impact that it had for
OL,11,Fme, as a motivational speaker I'm
OL,12,Fsupposed to be resilient.
OL,14,F"There was four seconds when I
OL,15,Fconsidered ending it all, four
OL,16,Fseconds, that's how hard it got.
OL,18,F"People end up putting these daft
OL,19,Fcomments online believing it's just a
OL,20,Fcomment online, but there's someone
OL,21,Fbehind that.
OL,26,@vD@AOUzD@AOU
