OL,4,Ccyberstalking
OL,6,F"When you have thousands of posts, day
OL,7,Fin day out, and the worst thing about
OL,8,Fit, it was like a modern day witch-
OL,9,Fhunt, she was weaponising and she was
OL,10,Fgalvanising people to it, and I had to
OL,11,Fdefend myself yet I couldn't defend
OL,12,Fmyself."
OL,14,FNaomi Timperley got a similar
OL,15,Ftreatment after she warned Wall to
OL,16,Fstop attacking fellow business people
OL,17,Fonline.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
