OL,3,CWoman sentenced after 'horrific'
OL,4,Ccyberstalking
OL,6,FMs Timperley said: "It's been
OL,7,Fhorrific... It's been mentally and
OL,8,Fphysically draining on me, my friends,
OL,9,Fand my family.
OL,11,F"I wouldn't wish it on my worst enemy."
OL,13,FBoth victims say they initially had
OL,14,Fcompassion for Wall, but "she eroded
OL,15,Fthat".
OL,17,FNaomi went to the police to try and
OL,18,Fget the harassment to stop, but both
OL,19,Fvictims say it has been a battle to
OL,20,Fget the case to court. They say
OL,21,Fstalking is not taken seriously enough.
