OL,6,FAlthough Wall has finally been
OL,7,Fconvicted in court, the posts remain
OL,8,Fonline, damaging their reputations.
OL,10,FNaomi said the social media companies
OL,11,Fdid "absolutely nothing".
OL,13,FShe said: "If I was breastfeeding a
OL,14,Fchild they would probably remove that
OL,15,Fpicture. But you can be abused by
OL,16,Fsomebody and complain about it, very
OL,17,Fdefamatory stuff and false
OL,18,Faccusations, and they never did
OL,19,Fanything."
