OL,6,FSocial media is an integral part of
OL,7,FTimperley's business, so she says she
OL,8,Fis even more upset at the lack of
OL,9,Fresponse from the platforms.
OL,11,FShe said: "They've been a massive part
OL,12,Fof my business life and I actively
OL,13,Fencourage people to use them.
OL,15,F"But I think it's really really sad
OL,16,Fthat as a victim of a crime I haven't
OL,17,Fbeen protected by them."
